<h2>Hostname Configuration</h2>

<% form_for :hostname do |f| %>

<table class="system" style="text-align: left; width: auto;">
  <tr>
    <th>Hostname</th>
    <th>Domain</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><%= f.text_field "hostname" %></td>
    <td><%= f.text_field "domain" %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

  <%= submit_tag "Save", { :id => 'save' } %>
<% end %>

<%# render :partial => 'reloading' if flash[:notice] %>

<div class="example">
  <h2>Information</h2>

  <h4>Licensing</h4>
  <p>If you have activated the mailserver, the license key is tied to the hostname of the server. If you
    change hostname, it will update the licensing information at update.allardsoft.com so a connection
    there is requried. If you haven't activated the server, it won't try to connect to update.allardsoft.com.</p>
</div>
